=== 開發 ===
2016年1月22日，[[福斯廣播公司|FOX]]宣布預訂由{{link-en|傑若米·史雷特|Jeremy Slater}}改編自1971年{{link-en|威廉·彼得·布拉蒂|William Peter Blatty}}的小說《{{link-en|大法師 (小說)|The Exorcist (novel)|大法師}}》之電視試播集，並由史雷特、{{link-en|詹姆斯·G·羅賓森|James G. Robinson|詹姆斯·羅賓森}}、{{link-en|大衛·C·羅賓森|David C. Robinson|大衛·羅賓森}}與芭芭拉·沃爾（{{lang|en|Barbara Wall}}）共同擔任執行製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/22/exorcist-tv-fox|title=The Exorcist TV series in the works at Fox|work=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|date=2016-01-22|first=James|publisher=[[時代公司|時代公司]]|accessdate=2016-05-16|last=Hibberd|archive-date=2016-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513191003/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/22/exorcist-tv-fox|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Laura">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/the-exorcist-tv-series-pilot-fox-1201686653/|title=‘The Exorcist’ Pilot Ordered at Fox with Modern Twist|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|date=2016-01-22|last=Prudom|first=Laura|accessdate=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503073431/http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/the-exorcist-tv-series-pilot-fox-1201686653/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年2月2日，宣布[[電影|電影]]《[[猿人爭霸戰：猩凶革命|猩球崛起]]》[[電影導演|導演]][[魯伯特·瓦耶特|魯伯特·瓦耶特]]將執導本劇試播集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/rupert-wyatt-direct-the-exorcist-pilot-jeff-blitz-the-trail-1201694966/|title=Rupert Wyatt To Direct ‘The Exorcist’ Pilot; Jeff Blitz Set For ‘The Trail’|work=Deadline.com|author=Denise Petski|date=2016-02-02|accessdate=2016-10-12|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018195641/http://deadline.com/2016/02/rupert-wyatt-direct-the-exorcist-pilot-jeff-blitz-the-trail-1201694966/|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月10日，FOX正式宣布系列預訂本劇。<ref name="Series Order"/>5月12日，宣布第1季將於[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]拍攝。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-the-exorcist-tv-series-fox-filming-in-chicago-20160511-column.html|title=Fox's 'The Exorcist,' 'A.P.B.' to film in Chicago for next TV season|work=[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]|accessdate=2016-05-12|5=|date=2016-05-11|first=Nina|last=Metz|publisher={{link-en|tronc|tronc}}|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512103551/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-the-exorcist-tv-series-fox-filming-in-chicago-20160511-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年5月12日，FOX宣布續訂第2季。<ref name="Season 2 Renewed">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/05/the-exorcist-renewed-season-2-fox-1202092418/|title='The Exorcist' Renewed For Season 2 By Fox|last=Petski|first=Denise|work=Deadline.com|date=2017-05-12|accessdate=2017-05-12|archive-date=2017-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170513075041/http://deadline.com/2017/05/the-exorcist-renewed-season-2-fox-1202092418/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年5月11日，FOX正式宣布取消劇集。<ref name="Canceled">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-exorcist-canceled-fox-2-seasons-1202381724/|title=‘The Exorcist’ Canceled By Fox After 2 Seasons|work=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2018-05-11|accessdate=2018-05-11|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511232242/http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-exorcist-canceled-fox-2-seasons-1202381724/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

