rk=TVLine|first=Michael|last=Slezak|archive-date=2016-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513043455/http://tvline.com/2016/03/02/the-exorcist-tv-series-cast-alfonso-herrera-ben-daniels/|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔日，宣布《[[無境之獸|無境之獸]]》庫特·席爾瓦（{{lang|en|Kurt Egyiawan}}）將飾演[[梵蒂岡|梵蒂岡]]聯繫人員班奈特神父。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/geneva-carr-cast-cbs-drama-pilot-bull-1201713979/|title=Geneva Carr Joins CBS Drama Pilot ‘Bull’; Fox’s ‘The Exorcist’ Adds Kurt Egyiawan|work=Deadline.com|accessdate=2016-05-11|date=2016-03-03|first=Denise|last=Petski|archive-date=2018-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628233605/https://deadline.com/2016/03/geneva-carr-cast-cbs-drama-pilot-bull-1201713979/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Davis and Egyiawan"/>3月7日，宣布[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡]]得主[[吉娜·戴維斯|吉娜·戴維斯]]將重返小螢幕，於本劇飾演家庭遭到惡靈迫害的安潔拉·蘭斯。<ref name="Davis and Egyiawan">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/geena-davis-the-exorcist-fox-pilot-1201724304/|title=Geena Davis Cast in Fox’s ‘Exorcist’ Reboot Pilot|work=綜藝雜誌|date=2016-03-07|accessdate=2016-05-11|first=Elizabeth|last=Wagmeister|archive-date=2016-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513004310/http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/geena-davis-the-exorcist-fox-pilot-1201724304/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月10日，宣布於試播集中客串演出的[[阿蘭·拉克|亞倫·拉克]]將被提升為主要演員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/the-exorcist-alan-ruck-promoted-regular-fox-series-1201770799/|title=‘The Exorcist’: Alan Ruck Upped To Regular On New Fox Series|accessdate=2016-05-11|date=2016-06-10|work=Deadline.com|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611151909/http://deadline.com/2016/06/the-exorcist-alan-ruck-promoted-regular-fox-series-1201770799/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

